SIMPLE: instead
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Instead
<hw>In*stead"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> + <ets>stead</ets> place.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>In the place or room; -- usually followed by
<xex>of</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let thistles grow of wheat.</q> <rj><qau>Job xxxi.
40.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Absalom made Amasa captain of the host <qex>instead</qex> of
Joab.</q> <rj><qau>2 Sam. xvii. 25.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Equivalent; equal to; -- usually with
<xex>of</xex>.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This very consideration to a wise man is <qex>instead</qex> of a
thousand arguments, to satisfy him, that in those times no such thing
was believed.</q> <rj><qau>Tillotson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insteep</ent>⟦br⟧
